metadata.name: Karaktero #1: Flaming Samurai
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Mad Monk, Karaktero smart contract (Manifold), 2022

Karakteroj is a collection of Karaktero by Mad Monk. AI + Emotional + Expressive + Mad. It has emojis, samurais, cowgirls, werewolves, apes, Betty and some cats along with some other dogs. What more would you want? Get your Karaktero and set your mind free.
